{"tid":2510240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"十二港人案 約40張旁聽籌將於下午一時開始派發","createTime":"2021-04-30T04:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:48:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c6389a86f3b65eba0aab9cdb9eb4e3c9b897bd93","tid":2510240,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15365&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=61ce5202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15365</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#十二港人案 #新案件<br />\n<br />\n案件詳情 (<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210429/CARLK6E6QVBZDGGATFGQU45RJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210429%2FCARLK6E6QVBZDGGATFGQU45RJU%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=3e158a74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210429%2FCARLK6E6QVBZDGGATFGQU45RJU%2F&h=2ae1771d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210429/CARLK6E6QVBZDGGATFGQU45RJU/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n在東區裁判法院第一庭【今日14:30】進行的聆訊，司法機構將會安排9樓11庭作為法庭的延伸部份，即時轉播有關案件的法庭程序。<br />\n<br />\n約40張紫色籌將預留予公眾人士，所有籌會以先到先得的形式於【13:00】開始派發。"},{"pid":"9f07645cbaaa3d6eec27df08e822d46e1b6e4cc4","tid":2510240,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1300"},{"pid":"d9752ae4b648b7565c7173756f7e357466a8691a","tid":2510240,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f07645cbaaa3d6eec27df08e822d46e1b6e4cc4","tid":2510240,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces